tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE FilterData (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR,
    country VARCHAR,
    condition VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE condition_filtering (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
condition_name VARCHAR,
filter_type VARCHAR,
training_method VARCHAR,
data_source VARCHAR);

CREATE TABLE dataset_columns (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
column_name VARCHAR,
data_type VARCHAR,
is_feature BOOLEAN,
is_label BOOLEAN);

CREATE TABLE model_parameters (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
parameter_name VARCHAR,
parameter_type VARCHAR,
default_value VARCHAR);

CREATE TABLE model_training (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
model_type VARCHAR,
dataset_id INT,
parameter_id INT);

CREATE TABLE trained_models (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
model_name VARCHAR,
accuracy FLOAT,
precision FLOAT);

CREATE TABLE model_validation (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
model_id INT,
validation_date DATE,
validation_result BOOLEAN);
